<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Pinokio Create Bookmarklet</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      color-scheme: light dark;
      font-family: "SF Pro Text", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 24px 18px 48px;
      background: rgba(248, 250, 255, 0.92);
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    body.dark {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.96);
    }
    .page {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px 36px;
      box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
    }
    body.dark .page {
      background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.85);
      box-shadow: 0 50px 120px rgba(2, 6, 20, 0.65);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .bookmarklet-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, royalblue, royalblue);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(111, 76, 242, 0.32);
      cursor: grab;
    }
    .bookmarklet-button:active {
      cursor: grabbing;
    }
    .steps {
      list-style: decimal;
      margin: 0 0 0 20px;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .code-block {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 120px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
      background: rgba(248, 250, 255, 0.7);
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: inherit;
      resize: vertical;
    }
    body.dark textarea {
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
    }
    button.copy-btn {
      align-self: flex-start;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #fff;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25);
    }
    body.dark button.copy-btn {
      background: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.85);
      color: #0f172a;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);
    }
    small {
      opacity: 0.75;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      body {
        padding: 18px 12px 36px;
      }
      .page {
        padding: 24px;
        border-radius: 16px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="<%= theme %>">
  <main class="page">
    <header>
      <h1>Pinokio “Create” Bookmarklet</h1>
      <p>Drop this bookmarklet onto your bookmarks bar. Clicking it on any site opens Pinokio’s Create modal with that page’s URL pre-filled in the prompt.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
      <a class="bookmarklet-button" href="<%- bookmarkletHref %>">Pinokio Create</a>
      <small>Tip: Drag the button to your bookmarks bar, or right-click → “Add to Favorites/Bookmarks”.</small>
    </section>

    <section>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li>Make sure your bookmarks bar is visible (View → Toolbars → Bookmarks Toolbar, or press <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>/<kbd>Cmd</kbd> + <kbd>Shift</kbd> + <kbd>B</kbd>).</li>
        <li>Drag the “Pinokio Create” button above to the bar.</li>
        <li>When you are on a page you want to automate, click the bookmark. Pinokio will open at <code><%= baseUrl %>/create</code> with the current page URL in the prompt field.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="code-block">
      <strong>Manual option</strong>
      <p>If dragging doesn’t work, create a new bookmark manually and paste the code below as the URL.</p>
      <textarea id="bookmarklet-code" readonly><%- bookmarkletHref %></textarea>
      <button type="button" class="copy-btn" data-copy>Copy bookmarklet code</button>
      <small class="copy-status" hidden>Copied!</small>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    (function() {
      const copyBtn = document.querySelector('[data-copy]');
      const textarea = document.getElementById('bookmarklet-code');
      const status = document.querySelector('.copy-status');

      if (!copyBtn || !textarea) {
        return;
      }

      copyBtn.addEventListener('click', async () => {
        const text = textarea.value;
        try {
          if (navigator.clipboard && navigator.clipboard.writeText) {
            await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
          } else {
            textarea.select();
            document.execCommand('copy');
          }
          if (status) {
            status.hidden = false;
            status.textContent = 'Copied!';
            setTimeout(() => {
              status.hidden = true;
            }, 1800);
          }
        } catch (error) {
          if (status) {
            status.hidden = false;
            status.textContent = 'Copy failed. Please copy manually.';
            setTimeout(() => {
              status.hidden = true;
              status.textContent = 'Copied!';
            }, 2600);
          }
        }
      });
    })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
